dct_title_s: Hoboken and proposed Weehawkin, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map of Hoboken borough, North Bergen and the proposed new township of Weehawken, New Jersey. The existing communities are bordered in red (for Hoboken) and yellow (for North Bergen) while the future Weehawken land is shaded in green. Weehawken Township was officially formed in 1859.
